cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with visual question answering, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method incorporates probabilistic deep learning methods (cs.AI) and uses gradients for certainty estimates (cs.LG). The attention maps generated by the method are compared with human attention regions (cs.IR).
